{"tid":1485302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"次次一到去留問題 就有人話勸人走＝割席","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:30:19.000Z","uid":90601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"419cc046fe87b879c880fcb1d1f6832537001dd0","tid":1485302,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:48:08.000Z","msg":"講左幾多次，每個人既危機感唔同<br />\n想前線走既，係希望大家目標完成唔好冒險<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係要同前線／勇武割席</span><br />\n<br />\n出過黎既，絕對唔會屌前線，絕對明白做得前線都係熱血，的確係要人勸先走<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以先要大大力勸佢地</span><br />\n一個手足唔得，就搵夠十個手足<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔明，請理解大家都係一片好意，無話邊個割邊個，正如從來無勇武割唔衝既人<br />\n去到今時今日，200萬人大家坐埋一條船，香港一條人，唔會有人再割<br />\n<br />\n如果你係分化既<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母番你老母個閪度啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"cea8a67979e1a1d25759461fc567cfb2300008a5","tid":1485302,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba34cfd920c401d6024e840fcb5ed7c420832cd3","tid":1485302,"uid":241458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"淋完雨好返屋企沖涼喇<br />\n現場手足如果勸完都唔走就自己走啦，佢地見冇人都會走<br />\n<br />\n停止捉鬼，由得啲鬼自己OT啦"},{"pid":"0318b585e54ddb7d8b0ec2cb4ec13e0d91a29fbc","tid":1485302,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0afe924ee8d29546dca7a60aef04deb481c7d4","tid":1485302,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc4809de197194319cdc8b9b1eb772465604421","tid":1485302,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4d977b08a4db94142547c2db5711bf5f5b1a3c","tid":1485302,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}